Class RedeemRewardPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.base.BaseFixture
      • com.pom.crimson.base.BasePage
        • com.pom.crimson.pages.RedeemRewardPage

  • public class RedeemRewardPage
extends BasePage
    This is the Page Class for Rewards page in the mobile application.
    User can navigate to this page by going to:

    Profile menu from home page Tab bar
    Click on Rewards menu from the profile menus
    This page class contains MobileElements on this page and functions to simulate interactions with these elements.
    Author:
    Balaji.Sridharan
